01632,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T09:17:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個班開屌泛民冇人敢入</blockquote><br />\n打手樓主夠唔夠膽答下我啲問題</blockquote><br />\n你行撚開啦<br />\n依加講緊點解唔屌埋保皇你拋一埋泛民點點點做乜？<br />\n咁就係唔屌埋保皇狗既原因？<br />\n你收左保皇狗幾錢啊？"},{"pid":"90276c4fe7202f66035a8b5f4ed93085085a6c69","tid":501632,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T09:19:07.000Z","msg":"大家睇到啦<br />\n問佢點解唔屌埋保皇狗<br />\n答唔到<br />\n拋一堆點解要屌泛民既理由出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n十足五毛spin"},{"pid":"712dc0bcf6432c7fc14c9a3f91aa186d04349a75","tid":501632,"uid":30569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T09:58:08.000Z","msg":"保皇狗係仆街冚家剷<br />\n唔代表泛民唔係"},{"pid":"5ebf0848e1d3bbcbf037c9b54327d59f729b76a4","tid":501632,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T09:59:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">偽本土五毛<br />\n全面進場</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce73b1810efaa649c270f4ad19a57d4bf027461f","tid":501632,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T09:59:55.000Z","msg":"土共同泛民一樣啫，真係唔洗爭喎"}]}